<!--<h4>Beam-1.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> jjana saṁstuta <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> daya manuttama pa <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> darpabīraṁ madhuvarājana <unclear>na</unclear>ltadoḍuttarōttaraṁ śamedame rūpu <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> vṛddhi bhāgya vye(ḷu)mevabhimānameṁba guṇavītanoḷoppidavantu negaḻvadaṁ <g type="ddanda">.</g>
</p>

<!--<h4>Beam-2.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> śītakaranaṁtu mṛdaṁge kumārageṁtu śakrarige jayantaneṁtu raghuvige raghūdbhava nōtu (parimaḷa) <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> (sa) nārjjisidante vāsudēva(ne)ge tanūjanāgi madhusūdhana nārjjisidanegaḷte yaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<!--<h4>Beam-3.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>Anavadyākṛtiyiṁ prabhutva guṇadiṁ satyōptayiṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ganamaśuddhā caritradiṁ vibhuvasu <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> sakaḷa nētrādhāranāgiṟda mā <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> diṁ dhātrige vāsudēvanesedaṁ karṇnāṭa vaṁśōdbhavaṁ <g type="ddanda">.</g>
</p>

<!--<h4>Beam-4.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>vipuḷa śrīstanakuṁkumāṁkita viśēśā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> kanmāḷaṁ bhāratīlapanāḷōkana darppaṇaṁ nijayaśōvalli vṛtāśāmadadvipa saṁdōhanudātta
<lb n="2"/>(pa)ntāḻdaṁ mikka kāśyapa gōtrammadhusūdhanaṁ parahita vyāpāra pārāyaṇaṁ [<g type="ddanda">.</g>]
</p>

